title.narrative: Second Turkey Access to Finance for Small and Medium Enterprises Project

description.narrative: The project's main development objective is to broaden and deepen the access of Turkish small and medium enterprises to medium- and long-term finance, with a view to ultimately contributing to an expansion of productive activities and job creation.
